    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine currently runs but has significant oil leaks and a noticeable knock, while the transmission slips during gear changes. The exterior has extensive rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functioning electronics. It will likely require towing and major repairs before it can be used as a reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 6500.0,
