      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for a fantastic project opportunity! This vehicle is the perfect choice for a DIY enthusiast or mechanic looking for a budget-friendly entry into their next restoration. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a great foundation for someone ready to put in the work and bring it back to life. It's priced to sell and ready for a fresh start!",
